, Virginia]]|oclc=240192}}\n\n==External links==\n{{div col|colwidth=33em}}\n* {{cite web|url=https://www.novaparks.com/parks/washington-and-old-dominion-railroad-regional-park|title=Washington & Old Dominion Railroad Regional Park|location=[[Ashburn, VA]]|publisher=[[NOVA Parks]]|accessdate=September 27, 2017}}\n* [http://www.wodfriends.org/ The Friends of the Washington & Old Dominion Trail official website] Retrieved September 27, 2017.\n* {{cite web|url=http://geocities.com/Yosemite/Trails/9401|title=Unofficial Page of The Washington & Old Dominion Trail|publisher=RailServe.com by Christopher Muller|date=May 30, 2009|accessdate=August 5, 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050324091509/http://geocities.com/Yosemite/Trails/9401|archive-date=March 24, 2005|url-status=dead}}\n* {{cite web|url=http://geocities.com/Yosemite/Trails/9401/biketrails.html|title=Intersecting Bike Trails|publisher=Unofficial Page of The Washington & Old Dominion Trail|date=May 30, 2009|accessdate=August 5, 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050324091509/http://geocities.com/Yosemite/Trails/9401/biketrails.html|archive-date=March 24, 2005|url-status=dead}}\n* {{cite web|author=[http://www.blogger.com/profile/03930267735169346620 Heil, Jeffrey]|url=http://yellowbiketales.blogspot.com/2008/02/washington-old-dominion-trail-in.html|title=Washington & Old Dominion Trail in Virginia|work=yellowbiketales|date=February 13, 2008|accessdate=December 15, 2010}} Description of W&OD Trail and surrounding areas, published in ''Spokes'', September 2006.\n* [https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/video/2008/06/11/VI2008061102438.html Paul McCray (former Manager, W&OD Regional Park) discussing history of W&OD Trail in Uenuma, F, \"Two Decades Along the W&OD Trail\", Washington Post video] ''in'' [https://web.archive.org/web/20130719044058/http://www.washingtonpost/ Washington Post website.]  Retrieved June 20, 2008.\n* [http://www.hmdb.org/results.asp?SeriesID=18  \"Washington 