.8875844|-77.1634462|scale:500_source:wikimapia|format=dms|name=Coal trestle (Washington & Old Dominion Railroad)}}\n|-\n| Crossing of Little Falls Road\n| Arlington County\n| {{convert|5.9|mi|km}}\n| {{convert|325|ft}}\n| {{coord|38.888313|-77.165928|type:landmark|format=dms|name=Crossing of W&OD Trail and Little Falls Road}}\n|-\n| W&OD Railroad station mile marker post\n| City of Falls Church\n| {{convert|5.9|mi|km}}\n| {{convert|325|ft}}\n| {{coord|38.888471|-77.166426|type:landmark|format=dms|name=W&OD Railroad station mile marker post}}\n|-\n| Former site of [[Washington and Old Dominion Railroad#Stations|West Falls Church W&OD Railroad station]]\n| City of Falls Church\n| {{convert|6.9|mi|km}}\n| {{convert|388|ft}}\n| {{coord|38.891649|-77.185226|type:landmark|format=dms|name=Site of West Falls Church station of W&OD Railroad}}\n|-\n| Trail bridge over West Broad Street ([[Virginia State Route 7|VA Route 7]])\n| City of Falls Church\n| {{convert|7.0|mi|km}}\n| {{convert|388|ft}}\n| {{coord|38.891768|-77.185972|type:landmark|format=dms|name=W&OD Trail bridge over West Broad Street (VA Route 7)}}\n|-\n| Trail and Virginia Lane bridge over I-66 and [[Washington Metro]]\n| Fairfax County\n| {{convert|8.4|mi|km}}\n| {{convert|453|ft}}\n| {{coord|38.890995|-77.2106|type:landmark|format=dms|name=Virginia Lane bridge over I-66 and Metrorail}}\n|-\n| Trail bridge over I-495 (Capital Beltway)\n|Fairfax County\n| {{convert|8.9|mi|km}}\n| {{convert|417|ft}}\n| {{coord|38.890478|-77.217863|type:landmark|format=dms|name=W&OD Trail bridge over I-495 (Capital Beltway)}}\n|-\n| Sandburg Street, Dunn Loring\n| Fairfax County\n| {{convert|9.1|mi|km}}\n| {{convert|417|ft}}\n| {{coord|38.8916257|-77.2223264|type:landmark|format=dms|name=Sandburg Street (Dunn Loring)}}\n|-\n| [[Northern Virginia trolleys#Remnants of the Fairfax line|Washington-Virginia Railway bridge abutments]]\n| Town of Vienna\n| {{convert|10.4|mi|km}}\n| {{convert|447|ft}}\n| {{coord|38.89988|-77.245718|type:landmark|format=dms|name=Washington-Virginia Railway bridge abutments}}\n|-\n| [[Freeman Store and Museum (Vienna, Virginia)|Freeman Store and Museum]]\n| Town of Vienna\n| {{convert|11.6|mi|km}}\n| {{convert|376|ft}}\n| {{coord|38.903357|-77.265113|type:landmark|format=dms|name=Freeman Store and Museum}}\n|-\n| Railroad [[whistle post]] in Vienna Centennial Park\n| Town of Vienna\n| {{convert|11.7|mi|km}}\n| {{convert|376|ft}}\n| {{coord|38.9033584|-77.2655408|type:landmark|format=dms|name=Whistle post in Vienna Centennial Park}}\n|-\n| Vienna Caboose and Museum in Vienna Centennial Park\n| Town of Vienna\n| {{convert|11.7|mi|km}}\n| {{convert|376|ft}}\n| {{coord|38.903608|-77.265708|type:landmark|format=dms|name=Vienna Caboose and Museum}}\n|-\n| [[Washington and Old Dominion Railroad#Stations 2|Vienna W&OD Railroad Station and model railroad]]\n| Town of Vienna\n| {{convert|11.8|mi|km}}\n| {{convert|349|ft}}\n| {{coord|38.904142|-77.266974|type:landmark|format=dms|name=Vienna W&OD Railroad Station and model railroad}}\n|-\n| [[Washington and Old Dominion Railroad#Bridges|Trail bridge over Piney Branch]]\n| Fairfax County\n| {{convert|13.6|mi|km}}\n| {{convert|260|ft}}\n| {{coord|38.925642|-77.288381|type:landmark|format=dms|name=W&OD Trail bridge over Piney Branch}}\n|-\n| [[Washington and Old Dominion Railroad#Bridges|Trail bridge over Difficult Run]]\n| Fairfax County\n| {{convert|14.3|mi|km}}\n| {{convert|240|ft}}\n| {{coord|38.930942|-77.29834|type:landmark|format=dms|name=W&OD Trail Bridge over Difficult Run}}\n|-\n| Dulles Access Road and Dulles Toll Road [[Virginia State Route 267|(VA Route 267)]] bridges over trail\n| Fairfax County\n| {{convert|16.1|mi|km}}\n| {{convert|354|ft}}\n| {{coord|38.944607|-77.325618|type:landmark|format=dms|name=Dulles Access Road and Dulles Toll Road bridges over W&OD Trail}}\n|-\n| Crossing of Wiehle Avenue near [[Wiehle\u2013Reston East station|Wiehle-Reston East Metro Station]]\n| Fairfax County\n| {{convert|16.8|mi|km}}\n|